{"tid":1986320,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[抄襲狗] 做Designer抄襲抄到咁真係好無恥，俾人話侵權仲要死兜爛兜","createTime":"2020-04-23T18:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T05:07:26.000Z","uid":262673,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8c2e863a8cbf6b8950489886217639e5afd2d3","tid":1986320,"uid":262673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9CfNw4x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9CfNw4x.png&h=7648844c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n👆🏼日安小熊個IG： good_day_bear<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家記得瘋狂留言洗佢版＋<strong>Report佢個IG</strong>，推到收撚皮為止！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span><br />\n<br />\n最近台灣創作界都喺度講關於抄襲問題，就連香港人都睇到。<br />\n有個台灣Designer叫日安小熊，佢最新推出嘅4款紙膠帶作品抄襲日本原創者，抄到應一應。不論係圖案Pattern、文字排版、色調定係包裝圓標label，都係抄日本原作者Yohaku ヨハク嘅風格去設計，抄到十足十。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1QzeWwd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1QzeWwd.png&h=beb33973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本原作者Yohaku ヨハク嘅設計係咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFbpzxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFbpzxV.png&h=21749f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZF9LEB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZF9LEB.png&h=b4a19604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6aYDZE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6aYDZE.png&h=15cc123b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gatn5EF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgatn5EF.png&h=c295591f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最弊連Yohaku ヨハク 都忍唔住喺日安小熊個IG留言話啲Style好似佢，仲要留言唔止一次。話咁易就篤穿佢抄人，食相難睇到極點，真係柒出國際，實在係文創界恥辱！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWLxJcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWLxJcq.jpg&h=297f6636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivUiDLK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivUiDLK.jpg&h=39656b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giHcJco.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiHcJco.jpg&h=2f2ce8af&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係嗰隻熊完全無視留言，繼續出新紙膠帶預購兼搞埋抽獎，咁樣夠膽做唔夠膽認，真係好撚仆街，難怪俾網民話食人血饅頭食到懵撚咗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRBhabR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRBhabR.jpg&h=0afeb461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有眼利嘅網民睇到個創作者點抄襲日本原創者，仲要人俾錢買佢嘅抄抄子膠帶！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1CcJx9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1CcJx9.jpg&h=37377691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解釋即掩飾，兜嚟兜去整色整水都係話自己冇抄襲啦，真係極度卑鄙無恥下流賤格！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TaTGBT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTaTGBT6.jpg&h=8e210387&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗番起做插畫設計出Product，睇得出有部份創作者真係左抄抄右抄抄咁，畫風照抄已經講都費事、改吓個排版，改吓換吓啲字粒，就可以當係自己設計嘅商品拎去賣到貴一貴，呃盡唔少鍾意文具精品、「見到靚就買」嘅人俾錢俾喺呢啲人血饅頭身上。<br />\n唔好話支那，香港同台灣都係有咁嘅情況。"},{"pid":"09b6a000877b2d5e0432e454428dfc9862378921","tid":1986320,"uid":210084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T19:00:47.000Z","msg":"我自己做原創都成日俾人抄嘢，好唔開心<br />\n啲抄襲狗究竟係咪全部都冇腦諗Design?"},{"pid":"c7e2275cb6f9a0669a2bcc67f8876e7ad674b266","tid":1986320,"uid":262673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b6a000877b2d5e0432e454428dfc9862378921","tid":1986320,"uid":210084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T19:00:47.000Z","msg":"我自己做原創都成日俾人抄嘢，好唔開心<br />\n啲抄襲狗究竟係咪全部都冇腦諗Design?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T01:57:05.000Z","msg":"明顯係啦<br />\n佢哋讀設計讀屎片咁"},{"pid":"c3a6da4ad0ad0ad22f4d9198a5fe9890da9af97d","tid":1986320,